1
00:00:07,333 --> 00:00:09,375
- EARTH...

2
00:00:09,417 --> 00:00:11,000
FIRE...

3
00:00:11,041 --> 00:00:12,750
AIR...

4
00:00:12,792 --> 00:00:15,250
WATER.

5
00:00:15,291 --> 00:00:19,250
ONLY THE AVATAR CAN MASTER
ALL FOUR ELEMENTS,

6
00:00:19,291 --> 00:00:22,000
AND BRING BALANCE
TO THE WORLD.

7
00:00:22,041 --> 00:00:24,041
[dramatic music]

8
00:00:27,375 --> 00:00:28,625
- A CHANCE ENCOUNTER
TURNS KORRA

9
00:00:28,667 --> 00:00:31,458
FROM PRO BENDING SPECTATOR
TO PRO BENDING STAR,

10
00:00:31,500 --> 00:00:33,166
WITH HER NEW TEAMMATES,
MAKO AND BOLIN,

11
00:00:33,208 --> 00:00:34,417
THE FIRE FERRETS
EARN A PLACE

12
00:00:34,458 --> 00:00:35,667
IN THE CHAMPIONSHIP
TOURNAMENT.

13
00:00:35,709 --> 00:00:38,375
BUT MEANWHILE,
AN ANTI-BENDING REVOLUTION BREWS

14
00:00:38,417 --> 00:00:39,875
IN REPUBLIC CITY.

15
00:00:39,917 --> 00:00:42,333
WHO ARE THE EQUALISTS,
AND WHAT NEFARIOUS PLAN

16
00:00:42,375 --> 00:00:43,959
DOES THE MYSTERIOUS MAN
BEHIND THE MASK

17
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:46,750
HAVE IN STORE FOR OUR HERO?

18
00:00:51,417 --> 00:00:54,125
[tranquil music]

19
00:00:54,166 --> 00:00:57,667
♪ ♪

20
00:00:57,709 --> 00:00:59,208
- WHAT'S THE BIG IDEA
WITH MAKING ME TRAIN

21
00:00:59,250 --> 00:01:01,083
THIS EARLY IN THE MORNING?

22
00:01:01,125 --> 00:01:03,083
THE MORNING IS EVIL.

23
00:01:03,125 --> 00:01:04,291
- WE'RE THE ROOKIES,

24
00:01:04,333 --> 00:01:06,166
SO WE GET THE WORST
TIME SLOT IN THE GYM.

25
00:01:06,208 --> 00:01:07,709
- AND YOU'RE
THE ROOKIEST OF US ALL.

26
00:01:07,750 --> 00:01:09,166
WE GOTTA GET YOU
UP TO SPEED

27
00:01:09,208 --> 00:01:10,542
IF WE WANT TO SURVIVE
IN THE TOURNAMENT.

28
00:01:10,583 --> 00:01:12,291
DEAL WITH IT.

29
00:01:12,333 --> 00:01:13,625
- YOU DEAL WITH IT.

30
00:01:13,667 --> 00:01:14,625
- OOH!

31
00:01:14,667 --> 00:01:16,166
UGH.

32
00:01:16,208 --> 00:01:19,959
- THERE ARE MY LITTLE
HARDWORKING STREET URCHINS.

33
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:21,417
[Pabu squeaks]

34
00:01:21,458 --> 00:01:24,166
IT'S AN HONOR TO FINALLY
MEET YOU, AVATAR.

35
00:01:24,208 --> 00:01:25,709
- AND YOU ARE?

36
00:01:25,750 --> 00:01:27,417
- BUTAKHA.

37
00:01:27,458 --> 00:01:30,750
I RUN THIS WHOLE
PRO BENDING SHEBANG.

38
00:01:30,792 --> 00:01:33,375
HERE'S YOUR WINNINGS
FROM THE LAST MATCH.

39
00:01:33,417 --> 00:01:34,417
AH, AH, AH.

40
00:01:34,458 --> 00:01:35,792
BUT NOT SO FAST.

41
00:01:35,834 --> 00:01:38,291
FIRST, YOU OWE ME
FOR THE AVATAR'S NEW GEAR,

42
00:01:38,333 --> 00:01:41,208
GYM AND EQUIPMENT RENTALS
FOR LAST MONTH,

43
00:01:41,250 --> 00:01:43,792
RENT ON YOUR APARTMENT,

44
00:01:43,834 --> 00:01:47,834
AND A PERSONAL LOAN
FOR GROCERIES.

45
00:01:47,875 --> 00:01:50,417
- WHAT?
I'M A GROWING BOY.

46
00:01:50,458 --> 00:01:53,125
- OH, AND ONE MORE SMALL ITEM
OF BUSINESS.

47
00:01:53,166 --> 00:01:56,625
THE FIRE FERRETS NEED
TO ANTE UP 30,000 YUANS

48
00:01:56,667 --> 00:01:57,875
FOR THE CHAMPIONSHIP POT.

49
00:01:57,917 --> 00:02:00,083
- 30,000 YUANS?

50
00:02:00,125 --> 00:02:02,125
- SORRY, KIDS.

51
00:02:02,166 --> 00:02:03,458
YOU'VE GOT TILL
THE END OF THE WEEK

52
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:05,291
TO COME UP WITH THE DOUGH,
OR ELSE YOU'RE OUT

53
00:02:05,333 --> 00:02:08,125
OF THE TOURNAMENT.

54
00:02:08,166 --> 00:02:09,500
- YOU WOULDN'T
HAPPEN TO HAVE

55
00:02:09,542 --> 00:02:11,750
A SECRET AVATAR BANK ACCOUNT
OVERFLOWING WITH GOLD,

56
00:02:11,792 --> 00:02:12,875
WOULD YOU?

57
00:02:12,917 --> 00:02:14,291
- I GOT NOTHING.

58
00:02:14,333 --> 00:02:15,834
I'VE NEVER REALLY
NEEDED MONEY.

59
00:02:15,875 --> 00:02:17,750
I'VE ALWAYS HAD
PEOPLE TAKING CARE OF ME.

60
00:02:17,792 --> 00:02:19,917
- THEN I WOULDN'T SAY
YOU HAD NOTHING.

61
00:02:19,959 --> 00:02:21,792
- SORRY, I DIDN'T MEAN--

62
00:02:21,834 --> 00:02:23,959
- NO, IT'S ALL RIGHT,
IT'S JUST...

63
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:26,250
EVER SINCE
WE LOST OUR PARENTS,

64
00:02:26,291 --> 00:02:27,333
WE'VE BEEN ON OUR OWN.

65
00:02:27,375 --> 00:02:29,917
- I'M SO SORRY.
I DIDN'T KNOW.

66
00:02:29,959 --> 00:02:31,500
- SO ANYWAY...

67
00:02:31,542 --> 00:02:33,000
HOW ARE WE GOING
TO COME UP WITH THE MONEY?

68
00:02:33,041 --> 00:02:34,917
- OOH, OOH,
I GOT IT, I GOT IT.

69
00:02:34,959 --> 00:02:38,041
I'VE BEEN TRAINING PABU
TO DO CIRCUS TRICKS.

70
00:02:38,083 --> 00:02:39,417
NOW PEOPLE WOULD PAY
GOOD MONEY TO SEE THAT.

71
00:02:39,458 --> 00:02:40,750
- COME ON, BOLIN.

72
00:02:40,792 --> 00:02:42,583
WE NEED SERIOUS IDEAS.

73
00:02:42,625 --> 00:02:44,083
- I WAS SERIOUS.

74
00:02:44,125 --> 00:02:47,166
- DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
I'LL FIGURE SOMETHING OUT.

75
00:02:47,208 --> 00:02:52,625
I ALWAYS DO.

76
00:02:56,041 --> 00:02:57,709
- COME ONE, COME ALL.

77
00:02:57,750 --> 00:03:00,417
SEE PABU,
THE FANTASTIC FIRE FERRET,

78
00:03:00,458 --> 00:03:03,125
AS HE CROSSES
THE LADDER OF PERIL...

79
00:03:03,166 --> 00:03:05,667
[gasps]
UPSIDE DOWN.

80
00:03:05,709 --> 00:03:08,792
[Pabu licks noisily]

81
00:03:08,834 --> 00:03:09,792
PSST, PSST.

82
00:03:09,834 --> 00:03:11,125
[Pabu chitters]

83
00:03:11,166 --> 00:03:12,458
BIG FINISH, BUDDY.

84
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:14,166
STICK THE LANDING.

85
00:03:14,208 --> 00:03:16,041
TA-DAH!

86
00:03:16,083 --> 00:03:18,667
THANK YOU,
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN.

87
00:03:18,709 --> 00:03:21,000
YOU ARE TOO KIND.
SERIOUSLY, TOO KIND.

88
00:03:21,041 --> 00:03:22,792
YOU CAN COME BACK HERE
AND PUT MONEY RIGHT IN THIS--

89
00:03:22,834 --> 00:03:24,375
[coin rattles] OKAY.
THAT'S FINE. THAT'S FINE.

90
00:03:24,417 --> 00:03:28,625
1 YUAN DOWN, 29,999 TO GO.

91
00:03:28,667 --> 00:03:31,542
[engine revs and stops]

92
00:03:31,583 --> 00:03:34,458
- HEY, BOLIN.
IS THAT YOU?

93
00:03:34,500 --> 00:03:39,291
- OH, HEY, THERE,
"SHADY" SHIN.

94
00:03:39,333 --> 00:03:41,709
- HEARD YOU'RE A BIG TIME
PRO BENDING PLAYER NOW.

95
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:43,125
NOT BAD.

96
00:03:43,166 --> 00:03:45,041
- UH, THANKS.

97
00:03:45,083 --> 00:03:48,041
- SO LISTEN,
I GOT AN OFFER FOR YOU.

98
00:03:48,083 --> 00:03:52,333
"LIGHTNING BOLT" ZOLT IS LOOKING
TO HIRE SOME EXTRA MUSCLE.

99
00:03:52,375 --> 00:03:55,417
- UH, I DON'T KNOW, SHIN.

100
00:03:55,458 --> 00:03:57,917
MAKO TOLD ME TO STAY AWAY
FROM THE TRIPLE THREATS.

101
00:03:57,959 --> 00:04:00,583
- [scoffs] YOUR BROTHER
AIN'T THE BOSS OF YOU.

102
00:04:00,625 --> 00:04:03,125
IT'S JUST
A LITTLE SECURITY WORK.

103
00:04:03,166 --> 00:04:06,041
NOTHING CROOKED.

104
00:04:06,083 --> 00:04:09,917
- [excitedly gasps]

105
00:04:09,959 --> 00:04:12,125
- YOU GAME?

106
00:04:12,166 --> 00:04:13,500
[energy crackling]

107
00:04:17,083 --> 00:04:19,500
[whistle blows]

108
00:04:19,542 --> 00:04:21,834
- [sighs]

109
00:04:25,333 --> 00:04:27,583
BO,
I'M BACK.

110
00:04:27,625 --> 00:04:29,750
PICKED UP
YOUR FAVORITE DUMPLINGS.

111
00:04:29,792 --> 00:04:31,667
[sighs]

112
00:04:31,709 --> 00:04:33,709
HEY, I FOUND SOME WORK
DOWN AT THE POWER PLANT.

113
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:36,959
IT'S SOME DECENT MONEY.

114
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:38,959
BOLIN?

115
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:41,458
YOU HERE, BRO?

116
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:44,458
[zither music]

117
00:04:44,500 --> 00:04:48,125
♪ ♪

118
00:04:48,166 --> 00:04:53,250
HUH, I BET THE LITTLE LOVE BIRD
IS MAKING A HOUSE CALL.

119
00:04:53,291 --> 00:04:56,959
[wind rustling]

120
00:04:57,000 --> 00:05:00,250
- GOOD,
LIGHT ON YOUR FEET.

121
00:05:03,625 --> 00:05:05,583
OOH, HE'S CUTE.

122
00:05:05,625 --> 00:05:07,250
KORRA, IS THAT
THE HANDSOME FIREBENDER BOY

123
00:05:07,291 --> 00:05:08,709
THAT DRIVES YOU CRAZY?

124
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,709
- DOES HE DRIVE YOU CRAZY
IN A BAD WAY,

125
00:05:10,750 --> 00:05:12,750
OR DOES HE DRIVE YOU CRAZY,
LIKE YOU LIKE HIM?

126
00:05:12,792 --> 00:05:14,125
[ground thuds]

127
00:05:14,166 --> 00:05:15,458
- [clears throat]

128
00:05:15,500 --> 00:05:17,792
[girls giggling]
OH, HEY, MAKO.

129
00:05:17,834 --> 00:05:18,792
- YOU SEEN BOLIN?

130
00:05:18,834 --> 00:05:20,542
- NICE TO SEE YOU TOO.

131
00:05:20,583 --> 00:05:23,041
AND NO, I HAVEN'T
SEEN HIM SINCE PRACTICE.

132
00:05:23,083 --> 00:05:23,959
THINK SOMETHING'S WRONG?

133
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,834
- I DON'T KNOW.

134
00:05:25,875 --> 00:05:28,625
BOLIN HAS A KNACK FOR GETTING
INTO STUPID SITUATIONS.

135
00:05:28,667 --> 00:05:29,625
[sighs]
SEE YOU LATER.

136
00:05:29,667 --> 00:05:30,834
- WAIT.

137
00:05:30,875 --> 00:05:33,583
I COULD, UH,
HELP YOU LOOK FOR HIM.

138
00:05:33,625 --> 00:05:34,834
- NAH, I GOT IT.

139
00:05:34,875 --> 00:05:37,458
- HEY, COOL GUY,
LET ME HELP YOU.

140
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:39,542
WE CAN TAKE NAGA.
- WHO'S NAGA?

141
00:05:39,583 --> 00:05:42,500
- MY BEST FRIEND,
AND A GREAT TRACKER.

142
00:05:44,583 --> 00:05:47,834
- YOUR BEST FRIEND
IS A...POLAR BEAR DOG.

143
00:05:47,875 --> 00:05:50,125
SOMEHOW THAT
MAKES PERFECT SENSE.

144
00:05:50,166 --> 00:05:52,875
- I'LL TAKE THAT
AS A COMPLIMENT, CITY BOY.

145
00:06:01,500 --> 00:06:04,417
- WELL,
THIS IS HIS USUAL HANGOUT.

146
00:06:04,458 --> 00:06:07,000
[children laughing]
- YAY.

147
00:06:07,041 --> 00:06:08,458
- WHOA.

148
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:10,792
- YOU GUYS SEE MY BROTHER
AROUND HERE TODAY?

149
00:06:10,834 --> 00:06:11,834
- PERHAPS.

150
00:06:11,875 --> 00:06:13,750
MY MEMORY'S
A LITTLE...FOGGY.

151
00:06:13,792 --> 00:06:16,208
MAYBE YOU CAN HELP
CLEAR IT UP.

152
00:06:16,250 --> 00:06:20,208
- YOU'RE GOOD, SKOOCHY.
A REAL PRO.

153
00:06:20,250 --> 00:06:22,125
- YEAH, I'VE SEEN HIM.
- WHEN?

154
00:06:22,166 --> 00:06:24,917
- ABOUT NOON.
- WHAT WAS HE DOING?

155
00:06:24,959 --> 00:06:26,875
- HE WAS PERFORMING
SOME KIND OF MONKEY-RAT CIRCUS.

156
00:06:26,917 --> 00:06:29,417
AND THEN...

157
00:06:29,458 --> 00:06:32,208
- AND THEN WHAT?
WHY'D HE LEAVE?

158
00:06:32,250 --> 00:06:36,000
- "SHADY" SHIN SHOWED UP
AND FLASHED SOME SERIOUS CASH.

159
00:06:36,041 --> 00:06:37,917
BO TOOK OFF WITH HIM
IN HIS HOT ROD.

160
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:40,125
THE TRIPLE THREATS,
THE RED MONSOONS,

161
00:06:40,166 --> 00:06:41,583
THE AGNI KAIS...

162
00:06:41,625 --> 00:06:44,291
ALL THE TRIADS ARE MUSCLING UP
FOR SOMETHING REAL BIG.

163
00:06:44,333 --> 00:06:47,333
NOW THAT'S ALL
YOU'RE GETTING OUT OF ME.

164
00:06:47,375 --> 00:06:49,542
- WHAT'S HE TALKING ABOUT?

165
00:06:49,583 --> 00:06:51,458
- SOUNDS LIKE
THERE'S A TURF WAR BREWING,

166
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:54,458
AND BOLIN'S ABOUT TO GET CAUGHT
RIGHT IN THE MIDDLE OF IT.

167
00:06:59,375 --> 00:07:00,709
- SO WHERE ARE WE HEADED?

168
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,333
- THE TRIPLE THREAT TRIAD'S
HEADQUARTERS.

169
00:07:02,375 --> 00:07:04,625
HOPEFULLY BOLIN'S THERE
AND NOTHING'S GONE DOWN YET.

170
00:07:04,667 --> 00:07:06,041
- TRIPLE THREAT TRIAD?

171
00:07:06,083 --> 00:07:08,458
I BEAT UP SOME OF THOSE YAHOOS
WHEN I GOT INTO TOWN.

172
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:10,083
WHY WOULD BOLIN
GET TANGLED UP WITH--

173
00:07:10,125 --> 00:07:11,125
[Naga growls]

174
00:07:11,166 --> 00:07:13,125
WHOA, NAGA.

175
00:07:13,166 --> 00:07:18,583
[Pabu squeaks]

176
00:07:18,625 --> 00:07:19,583
- THAT'S PABU.

177
00:07:19,625 --> 00:07:21,166
[Naga barks]
- NO, NAGA.

178
00:07:21,208 --> 00:07:26,291
PABU'S A FRIEND,
NOT A SNACK.

179
00:07:26,333 --> 00:07:28,083
[Pabu chitters]

180
00:07:28,125 --> 00:07:29,500
- WE GOTTA HURRY.

181
00:07:33,208 --> 00:07:34,458
SOMETHING'S NOT RIGHT.

182
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:36,500
THERE ARE USUALLY THUGS
POSTED OUT FRONT.

183
00:07:36,542 --> 00:07:38,041
WE BETTER BE CAUTIOUS.

184
00:07:43,291 --> 00:07:45,166
[loud crash]

185
00:07:50,083 --> 00:07:52,083
BOLIN?
YOU IN HERE?

186
00:07:52,125 --> 00:07:55,000
[engine revs]

187
00:07:55,041 --> 00:07:58,917
[motorcycles rev]

188
00:07:58,959 --> 00:08:02,417
- [muffled grunting]

189
00:08:02,458 --> 00:08:04,583
- BOLIN!

190
00:08:06,709 --> 00:08:09,959
[wheels screech]

191
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,792
[both coughing]

192
00:08:11,834 --> 00:08:13,041
- NAGA, COME!

193
00:08:13,083 --> 00:08:15,625
[Naga panting]

194
00:08:15,667 --> 00:08:18,625
[dramatic music]

195
00:08:18,667 --> 00:08:26,333
♪ ♪

196
00:08:32,417 --> 00:08:37,250
[pavement rumbling]

197
00:08:37,291 --> 00:08:40,166
[motorcycle revs]

198
00:08:46,542 --> 00:08:47,834
[ropes whirl]

199
00:08:47,875 --> 00:08:50,959
- [gasps]

200
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,291
- [groans]

201
00:08:53,333 --> 00:08:54,500
- OHH.

202
00:09:04,709 --> 00:09:07,375
- [grunting]

203
00:09:10,875 --> 00:09:13,417
[groaning]

204
00:09:20,875 --> 00:09:23,208
- [groaning]

205
00:09:26,917 --> 00:09:29,000
- [groaning]

206
00:09:29,041 --> 00:09:30,834
- OOH...
- UH...

207
00:09:30,875 --> 00:09:33,333
[Naga growling]

208
00:09:33,375 --> 00:09:39,208
[ropes swishing]

209
00:09:39,250 --> 00:09:42,667
[growling]

210
00:09:42,709 --> 00:09:44,250
[roaring]

211
00:09:44,291 --> 00:09:48,834
[Pabu squeaking]

212
00:09:48,875 --> 00:09:51,792
[engine reving]

213
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,208
[grunts]

214
00:09:57,250 --> 00:10:00,083
UGH! I CAN'T BEND.

215
00:10:00,125 --> 00:10:01,875
[grunts]
I CAN'T BEND!

216
00:10:01,917 --> 00:10:03,792
- CALM DOWN,
IT'LL WEAR OFF.

217
00:10:03,834 --> 00:10:05,834
THOSE GUYS
WERE CHI-BLOCKERS.

218
00:10:05,875 --> 00:10:08,291
THEY'RE AMON'S HENCHMEN.

219
00:10:08,333 --> 00:10:10,625
- AMON? THAT ANTI-BENDING
GUY WITH THE MASK?

220
00:10:10,667 --> 00:10:13,291
- YEAH, HE'S THE LEADER
OF THE EQUALISTS.

221
00:10:13,333 --> 00:10:15,458
- WHAT DO THEY WANT
WITH THE TRIPLE THREATS?

222
00:10:15,500 --> 00:10:18,208
- WHATEVER IT IS,
IT CAN'T BE GOOD.

223
00:10:18,250 --> 00:10:24,083
I CAN'T BELIEVE BOLIN
GOT HIMSELF INTO THIS MESS.

224
00:10:24,125 --> 00:10:26,250
- MAKO, WE ARE GOING
TO SAVE YOUR BROTHER.

225
00:10:26,291 --> 00:10:29,166
I PROMISE YOU THAT.

226
00:10:30,667 --> 00:10:33,625
[melancholy music]

227
00:10:33,667 --> 00:10:41,625
♪ ♪

228
00:10:41,667 --> 00:10:42,625
[Naga panting]

229
00:10:42,667 --> 00:10:43,834
WE'VE BEEN OUT ALL NIGHT.

230
00:10:43,875 --> 00:10:45,125
NO SIGN OF HIM.

231
00:10:45,166 --> 00:10:48,709
- WE'VE GOTTA KEEP LOOKING.
BUT WHERE?

232
00:10:48,750 --> 00:10:51,667
- [gasps]
I HAVE AN IDEA.

233
00:11:01,375 --> 00:11:03,041
THE FIRST DAY
I GOT INTO TOWN,

234
00:11:03,083 --> 00:11:05,333
I RAN INTO AN EQUALIST
PROTESTER OVER THERE.

235
00:11:05,375 --> 00:11:07,125
- AND YOU THINK THEY'LL KNOW
WHERE BOLIN IS?

236
00:11:07,166 --> 00:11:10,125
- IT'S OUR
ONLY LEAD RIGHT NOW.

237
00:11:10,166 --> 00:11:13,125
[dispirited music]

238
00:11:13,166 --> 00:11:18,500
♪ ♪

239
00:11:18,542 --> 00:11:20,792
SO, WHY IS BOLIN
RUNNING AROUND

240
00:11:20,834 --> 00:11:22,667
WITH THE TRIPLE THREAT TRIAD,
ANYWAY?

241
00:11:22,709 --> 00:11:25,792
- WELL, WE--WE USED TO DO SOME
WORK FOR THEM BACK IN THE DAY.

242
00:11:25,834 --> 00:11:26,875
- WHAT?

243
00:11:26,917 --> 00:11:28,333
ARE YOU
SOME KIND OF CRIMINAL?

244
00:11:28,375 --> 00:11:29,959
- NO.

245
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,375
YOU DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

246
00:11:31,417 --> 00:11:33,709
I JUST RAN NUMBERS
FOR THEM AND STUFF.

247
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:35,375
WE WERE ORPHANS
OUT ON THE STREET.

248
00:11:35,417 --> 00:11:37,000
I DID WHAT I HAD
TO DO TO SURVIVE

249
00:11:37,041 --> 00:11:38,875
AND PROTECT MY LITTLE BROTHER.

250
00:11:38,917 --> 00:11:39,834
- I'M SORRY.

251
00:11:39,875 --> 00:11:43,917
IT MUST HAVE BEEN
REALLY HARD.

252
00:11:43,959 --> 00:11:47,291
CAN I ASK WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOUR PARENTS?

253
00:11:47,333 --> 00:11:49,500
- [sighs]

254
00:11:49,542 --> 00:11:52,125
THEY WERE MUGGED
BY A FIREBENDER.

255
00:11:52,166 --> 00:11:54,375
HE CUT THEM DOWN
RIGHT IN FRONT OF ME.

256
00:11:54,417 --> 00:11:57,000
I WAS EIGHT.

257
00:11:57,041 --> 00:11:58,250
- MAKO...

258
00:11:58,291 --> 00:12:01,250
- BOLIN'S THE ONLY FAMILY
I HAVE LEFT.

259
00:12:01,291 --> 00:12:04,000
IF ANYTHING HAPPENED TO HIM...

260
00:12:07,959 --> 00:12:10,834
- [over loudspeaker]
EQUALITY NOW!

261
00:12:10,875 --> 00:12:14,083
EQUALITY NOW!
WE WANT EQUALITY NOW!

262
00:12:14,125 --> 00:12:15,667
- HMM...
AHH!

263
00:12:15,709 --> 00:12:17,000
[stammers
and clears throat]

264
00:12:17,041 --> 00:12:19,208
- NON-BENDERS
OF REPUBLIC CITY.

265
00:12:19,250 --> 00:12:20,208
- THAT'S THE GUY.

266
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:21,750
- AMON CALLS YOU TO ACTION.

267
00:12:21,792 --> 00:12:23,709
TAKE BACK YOUR CITY.

268
00:12:23,750 --> 00:12:27,625
IT'S TIME FOR THE--
[gasps]

269
00:12:27,667 --> 00:12:28,875
IT'S YOU AGAIN.

270
00:12:28,917 --> 00:12:31,792
YOU CANNOT SILENCE ME,
AVATAR.

271
00:12:31,834 --> 00:12:33,417
[yelps]

272
00:12:33,458 --> 00:12:34,959
- SHUT YOUR YAPPER
AND LISTEN UP.

273
00:12:35,000 --> 00:12:36,875
MY FRIEND GOT KIDNAPPED
BY SOME CHI-BLOCKERS.

274
00:12:36,917 --> 00:12:38,291
WHERE'D THEY TAKE HIM?

275
00:12:38,333 --> 00:12:40,667
- I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

276
00:12:40,709 --> 00:12:43,083
- OH, I THINK YOU DO.

277
00:12:43,125 --> 00:12:44,333
[ground thuds]

278
00:12:44,375 --> 00:12:46,875
- WHOA--
- [groans]

279
00:12:53,208 --> 00:12:56,667
- "WITNESS THE REVELATION
TONIGHT, 9:00."

280
00:12:56,709 --> 00:12:58,583
WHAT'S THIS REVELATION?

281
00:12:58,625 --> 00:13:01,166
- NOTHING THAT CONCERNS
THE LIKES OF YOU TWO.

282
00:13:01,208 --> 00:13:02,583
[shrieks]

283
00:13:02,625 --> 00:13:04,125
- YOU BETTER BELIEVE
IT CONCERNS US.

284
00:13:04,166 --> 00:13:05,834
SPILL IT.

285
00:13:05,875 --> 00:13:08,000
- NO ONE KNOWS
WHAT THE REVELATION IS.

286
00:13:08,041 --> 00:13:10,583
AND I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT HAPPENED TO YOUR FRIEND.

287
00:13:10,625 --> 00:13:12,875
BUT IF HE'S A BENDER,
THEN MY BET IS

288
00:13:12,917 --> 00:13:14,208
HE'S GETTING
WHAT'S COMING TO HIM.

289
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:15,250
- WHERE'S IT HAPPENING?

290
00:13:15,291 --> 00:13:17,208
[whistle blowing]

291
00:13:17,250 --> 00:13:19,542
- HEY, WHAT'S GOING ON
OVER THERE?

292
00:13:19,583 --> 00:13:22,458
- THE AVATAR'S OPPRESSING US.
HELP!

293
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:27,208
- LET'S SCRAM.

294
00:13:30,041 --> 00:13:33,333
WHY DIDN'T THE EQUALISTS
PUT A LOCATION ON THESE?

295
00:13:33,375 --> 00:13:35,041
- PROBABLY BECAUSE THEY DON'T
WANT JUST ANYONE

296
00:13:35,083 --> 00:13:37,083
WALTZING INTO
THEIR BIG REVELATION.

297
00:13:37,125 --> 00:13:38,709
WHATEVER THAT IS.

298
00:13:38,750 --> 00:13:41,291
I BET THE INFORMATION
IS HIDDEN ON HERE SOMEHOW.

299
00:13:41,333 --> 00:13:42,583
LOOK AT THE BACKS.

300
00:13:42,625 --> 00:13:45,959
THERE'S FOUR DIFFERENT IMAGES.

301
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,625
- SO IT'S A PUZZLE?

302
00:13:47,667 --> 00:13:52,083
- YEAH...OF A MAP.

303
00:13:57,041 --> 00:13:58,417
BINGO.

304
00:13:58,458 --> 00:14:02,542
THAT MUST BE
WHERE IT'S GOING DOWN.

305
00:14:11,792 --> 00:14:13,208
- THIS IS THE PLACE.

306
00:14:20,250 --> 00:14:21,750
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

307
00:14:21,792 --> 00:14:24,125
- WE'LL ATTRACT
LESS ATTENTION THIS WAY.

308
00:14:24,166 --> 00:14:26,709
- THIS IS PRIVATE EVENT.

309
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:28,792
NO ONE GETS IN
WITHOUT AN INVITATION.

310
00:14:28,834 --> 00:14:32,250
- UH, INVITATION?

311
00:14:32,291 --> 00:14:36,000
- YOU MEAN THIS?

312
00:14:36,041 --> 00:14:40,250
- THE REVELATION IS UPON US,
MY BROTHER AND SISTER.

313
00:14:40,291 --> 00:14:43,250
[tense music]

314
00:14:43,291 --> 00:14:46,583
♪ ♪

315
00:14:46,625 --> 00:14:49,250
- I KNEW A LOT OF PEOPLE
HATED BENDERS,

316
00:14:49,291 --> 00:14:51,875
BUT I'VE NEVER SEEN
SO MANY IN ONE PLACE.

317
00:14:51,917 --> 00:14:55,166
KEEP YOUR EYES OUT FOR BOLIN.

318
00:14:58,709 --> 00:15:03,959
- PLEASE WELCOME YOUR HERO,
YOUR SAVIOR,

319
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,875
AMON!

320
00:15:05,917 --> 00:15:09,834
[cheers and applause]

321
00:15:09,875 --> 00:15:12,834
[sinister music]

322
00:15:12,875 --> 00:15:20,125
♪ ♪

323
00:15:20,166 --> 00:15:24,500
- MY QUEST FOR EQUALITY
BEGAN MANY YEARS AGO.

324
00:15:24,542 --> 00:15:27,959
WHEN I WAS A BOY,
MY FAMILY AND I LIVED

325
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,583
ON A SMALL FARM.

326
00:15:29,625 --> 00:15:33,166
WE WEREN'T RICH,
AND NONE OF US WERE BENDERS.

327
00:15:33,208 --> 00:15:36,875
THIS MADE US VERY EASY TARGETS
FOR THE FIREBENDER

328
00:15:36,917 --> 00:15:38,875
WHO EXTORTED MY FATHER.

329
00:15:38,917 --> 00:15:42,792
ONE DAY,
MY FATHER CONFRONTED THIS MAN,

330
00:15:42,834 --> 00:15:44,750
BUT WHEN HE DID...

331
00:15:44,792 --> 00:15:48,250
THAT FIREBENDER
TOOK MY FAMILY FROM ME...

332
00:15:48,291 --> 00:15:51,125
THEN HE TOOK MY FACE.

333
00:15:51,166 --> 00:15:52,542
[crowd gasps]

334
00:15:52,583 --> 00:15:58,041
I'VE BEEN FORCED TO HIDE BEHIND
A MASK EVER SINCE.

335
00:15:58,083 --> 00:15:59,375
AS YOU KNOW,

336
00:15:59,417 --> 00:16:02,709
THE AVATAR HAS RECENTLY
ARRIVED IN REPUBLIC CITY.

337
00:16:02,750 --> 00:16:05,166
[crowd boos loudly]

338
00:16:05,208 --> 00:16:06,792
AND IF SHE WERE HERE,

339
00:16:06,834 --> 00:16:09,500
SHE WOULD TELL YOU
THAT BENDING BRINGS BALANCE

340
00:16:09,542 --> 00:16:12,750
TO THE WORLD,
BUT SHE IS WRONG.

341
00:16:12,792 --> 00:16:15,709
THE ONLY THING BENDING
HAS BROUGHT TO THE WORLD

342
00:16:15,750 --> 00:16:17,166
IS SUFFERING.

343
00:16:17,208 --> 00:16:21,375
IT HAS BEEN THE CAUSE
OF EVERY WAR IN EVERY ERA,

344
00:16:21,417 --> 00:16:25,500
BUT THAT IS ABOUT TO CHANGE.

345
00:16:25,542 --> 00:16:30,291
I KNOW YOU HAVE BEEN WONDERING,
"WHAT IS THE REVELATION?"

346
00:16:30,333 --> 00:16:32,750
YOU ARE ABOUT
TO GET YOUR ANSWER.

347
00:16:32,792 --> 00:16:36,709
SINCE THE BEGINNING OF TIME,

348
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:40,417
THE SPIRITS HAVE ACTED
AS GUARDIANS OF OUR WORLD,

349
00:16:40,458 --> 00:16:43,333
AND THEY HAVE SPOKEN TO ME.

350
00:16:43,375 --> 00:16:46,834
THEY SAY THE AVATAR
HAS FAILED HUMANITY,

351
00:16:46,875 --> 00:16:51,417
THAT IS WHY THE SPIRITS
HAVE CHOSEN ME

352
00:16:51,458 --> 00:16:54,917
TO USHER IN
A NEW ERA OF BALANCE.

353
00:16:54,959 --> 00:16:57,375
THEY HAVE GRANTED ME A POWER

354
00:16:57,417 --> 00:17:02,083
THAT WILL MAKE EQUALITY
A REALITY--

355
00:17:02,125 --> 00:17:06,500
THE POWER TO TAKE
A PERSON'S BENDING AWAY...

356
00:17:06,542 --> 00:17:09,667
PERMANENTLY.

357
00:17:09,709 --> 00:17:11,250
- THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

358
00:17:11,291 --> 00:17:12,500
THERE'S NO WAY.

359
00:17:12,542 --> 00:17:14,083
- THIS GUY IS INSANE.

360
00:17:14,125 --> 00:17:16,625
- NOW FOR A DEMONSTRATION.

361
00:17:16,667 --> 00:17:20,250
PLEASE WELCOME
"LIGHTNING BOLT" ZOLT,

362
00:17:20,291 --> 00:17:23,041
LEADER OF
THE TRIPLE THREAT TRIAD,

363
00:17:23,083 --> 00:17:25,375
AND ONE OF
THE MOST NOTORIOUS CRIMINALS

364
00:17:25,417 --> 00:17:26,375
IN REPUBLIC CITY.

365
00:17:26,417 --> 00:17:27,959
[crowd boos]

366
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,959
- AH, BOO YOURSELF.

367
00:17:35,375 --> 00:17:36,792
- THERE'S BOLIN.

368
00:17:36,834 --> 00:17:38,750
- WAIT.
WE CAN'T FIGHT THEM ALL.

369
00:17:38,792 --> 00:17:40,667
WE NEED TO BE SMART
ABOUT THIS.

370
00:17:40,709 --> 00:17:42,291
- THEN COME UP WITH
A GAME PLAN,

371
00:17:42,333 --> 00:17:43,750
TEAM CAPTAIN.

372
00:17:43,792 --> 00:17:45,834
- ZOLT HAS AMASSED
A FORTUNE

373
00:17:45,875 --> 00:17:49,291
BY EXTORTING AND ABUSING
NON-BENDERS,

374
00:17:49,333 --> 00:17:53,375
BUT HIS REIGN OF TERROR
IS ABOUT TO COME TO AN END.

375
00:17:53,417 --> 00:17:56,000
NOW, IN THE INTEREST
OF FAIRNESS,

376
00:17:56,041 --> 00:18:00,834
I WILL GIVE ZOLT THE CHANCE
TO FIGHT TO KEEP HIS BENDING.

377
00:18:00,875 --> 00:18:03,208
- YOU'RE GOING
TO REGRET DOING THAT, PAL.

378
00:18:03,250 --> 00:18:07,333
[fire ball explodes]

379
00:18:07,375 --> 00:18:13,333
[electricity crackles]

380
00:18:13,375 --> 00:18:16,500
[loud explosions]

381
00:18:16,542 --> 00:18:19,250
[gasps]

382
00:18:19,291 --> 00:18:20,291
[groans]

383
00:18:20,333 --> 00:18:23,291
[dramatic music]

384
00:18:23,333 --> 00:18:28,917
♪ ♪

385
00:18:28,959 --> 00:18:34,291
[groans]

386
00:18:34,333 --> 00:18:35,542
[grunts]

387
00:18:35,583 --> 00:18:37,542
[audience murmurs in awe]

388
00:18:37,583 --> 00:18:40,000
WHAT--WHAT
DID YOU DO TO ME?

389
00:18:40,041 --> 00:18:44,000
- YOUR FIREBENDING IS GONE...
FOREVER.

390
00:18:44,041 --> 00:18:47,208
[audience gasps]

391
00:18:47,250 --> 00:18:50,750
THE ERA OF BENDING IS OVER.

392
00:18:50,792 --> 00:18:55,000
A NEW ERA OF EQUALITY
HAS BEGUN!

393
00:18:55,041 --> 00:18:56,291
[cheers and applause]

394
00:18:56,333 --> 00:18:57,166
- HMM?
HEY.

395
00:18:57,208 --> 00:18:58,583
OH...

396
00:18:58,625 --> 00:19:01,125
HUH...NO,
UGH!

397
00:19:01,166 --> 00:19:02,250
- ANY IDEAS YET?

398
00:19:02,291 --> 00:19:04,375
- I THINK SO.
SEE THOSE MACHINES?

399
00:19:04,417 --> 00:19:06,166
THEY'RE POWERED
BY WATER AND STEAM.

400
00:19:06,208 --> 00:19:08,125
IF YOU CREATE SOME COVER,
I CAN GRAB BOLIN

401
00:19:08,166 --> 00:19:09,291
WITHOUT ANYONE SEEING.

402
00:19:09,333 --> 00:19:10,667
THEN WE DUCK OUT OF HERE.

403
00:19:10,709 --> 00:19:11,875
- WORKS FOR ME.

404
00:19:11,917 --> 00:19:13,792
MAKO, GOOD LUCK.

405
00:19:13,834 --> 00:19:17,250
- YOU TOO.

406
00:19:17,291 --> 00:19:20,250
[suspenseful music]

407
00:19:20,291 --> 00:19:23,583
♪ ♪

408
00:19:23,625 --> 00:19:25,291
[wheel creaks]

409
00:19:25,333 --> 00:19:26,834
- [grunts]

410
00:19:26,875 --> 00:19:30,208
NO, IT'S NOT ENOUGH.

411
00:19:30,250 --> 00:19:31,625
- HEY, YOU.

412
00:19:31,667 --> 00:19:34,500
♪ ♪

413
00:19:34,542 --> 00:19:38,250
- [groaning]

414
00:19:38,291 --> 00:19:42,333
[cheers and applause]
- [gasps]

415
00:19:42,375 --> 00:19:44,333
- IS THERE A PROBLEM,
MY BROTHER?

416
00:19:44,375 --> 00:19:46,041
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING
BACK HERE?

417
00:19:46,083 --> 00:19:51,333
- UH, LOOKING FOR
THE BATHROOM?

418
00:19:51,375 --> 00:19:52,709
[clicks tool]

419
00:19:55,750 --> 00:19:58,083
- [grunting]

420
00:19:58,125 --> 00:19:59,458
[pipe clangs]

421
00:19:59,500 --> 00:20:01,250
- COME ON.

422
00:20:01,291 --> 00:20:02,458
[pipes clang]

423
00:20:05,291 --> 00:20:06,750
- [gasps]
WHOA--WHOA--

424
00:20:06,792 --> 00:20:08,625
[groans]

425
00:20:08,667 --> 00:20:12,417
- THANKS.
THIS SHOULD BE ENOUGH.

426
00:20:12,458 --> 00:20:14,208
- OOH.
[gasps]

427
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:16,750
[whimpering]

428
00:20:16,792 --> 00:20:18,083
[groans]

429
00:20:18,125 --> 00:20:22,458
[audience cheers]

430
00:20:22,500 --> 00:20:25,709
UH, HELLO.
AMON, SIR.

431
00:20:25,750 --> 00:20:29,583
I THINK THERE'S BEEN
A BIG MISUNDERSTANDING.

432
00:20:29,625 --> 00:20:34,458
[air whooshing]

433
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:37,458
[loud explosion]

434
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:41,417
[audience screaming]

435
00:20:46,375 --> 00:20:48,041
- [gasps]
UGH--

436
00:20:48,083 --> 00:20:49,333
- [screams]

437
00:20:49,375 --> 00:20:50,917
- BOLIN, YOU ALL RIGHT?

438
00:20:50,959 --> 00:20:54,333
- YES, MAKO!
I LOVE YOU.

439
00:20:54,375 --> 00:20:55,625
[door slams open]

440
00:21:03,667 --> 00:21:05,125
[electricity zapping]

441
00:21:05,166 --> 00:21:07,083
[both screaming]

442
00:21:07,125 --> 00:21:09,375
[groaning]

443
00:21:09,417 --> 00:21:10,500
[electricity crackles]

444
00:21:15,583 --> 00:21:17,709
- [groaning]

445
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:20,542
- UGH!

446
00:21:20,583 --> 00:21:21,583
YAH!

447
00:21:27,709 --> 00:21:29,667
[groaning]

448
00:21:29,709 --> 00:21:32,458
[screaming]

449
00:21:35,375 --> 00:21:37,208
- [grunts]

450
00:21:37,250 --> 00:21:40,083
[electricity crackles]

451
00:21:40,125 --> 00:21:42,667
[groans]

452
00:21:42,709 --> 00:21:46,166
[screaming]

453
00:21:46,208 --> 00:21:48,125
- YOU BENDERS NEED
TO UNDERSTAND

454
00:21:48,166 --> 00:21:51,417
THERE'S NO PLACE IN THE WORLD
FOR YOU ANYMORE.

455
00:21:51,458 --> 00:21:52,542
[pavement loudly cracks]

456
00:21:52,583 --> 00:21:55,333
[groans]

457
00:21:55,375 --> 00:21:57,625
[panting]

458
00:21:57,667 --> 00:21:59,041
- I WOULDN'T COUNT US OUT
JUST YET.

459
00:21:59,083 --> 00:22:00,125
- [groans]

460
00:22:00,166 --> 00:22:01,834
- [whistles]
NAGA!

461
00:22:01,875 --> 00:22:04,750
[Naga barks]

462
00:22:08,166 --> 00:22:10,500
- [screaming]

463
00:22:10,542 --> 00:22:13,041
AH! OH! YAH!
GUYS, STOP!

464
00:22:13,083 --> 00:22:14,875
I WANT...TO BE...
ON...YOUR BACK.

465
00:22:14,917 --> 00:22:18,500
- THE AVATAR--THAT'S HER.

466
00:22:18,542 --> 00:22:20,500
- LET HER GO.

467
00:22:20,542 --> 00:22:22,959
SHE'S THE PERFECT MESSENGER
TO TELL THE CITY

468
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:24,625
OF MY POWER.

469
00:22:31,959 --> 00:22:33,834
- THANK GOODNESS.

470
00:22:33,875 --> 00:22:35,625
I WAS JUST ABOUT
TO SEND OUT A SEARCH PARTY.

471
00:22:35,667 --> 00:22:37,417
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

472
00:22:37,458 --> 00:22:39,250
- MM-MM.

473
00:22:39,291 --> 00:22:41,458
- KORRA, WHAT HAPPENED?

474
00:22:41,500 --> 00:22:42,458
DID YOU FIND YOUR FRIEND?

475
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:44,500
- YES, BUT...

476
00:22:44,542 --> 00:22:46,917
I WAS AT AN EQUALIST RALLY.

477
00:22:46,959 --> 00:22:48,917
I SAW AMON.
- WHAT?

478
00:22:48,959 --> 00:22:52,083
- HE CAN TAKE
PEOPLE'S BENDING AWAY FOR GOOD.

479
00:22:52,125 --> 00:22:54,750
- THAT'S--THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

480
00:22:54,792 --> 00:22:57,458
ONLY THE AVATAR HAS EVER
POSSESSED THAT ABILITY.

481
00:22:57,500 --> 00:22:59,667
- BUT I SAW HIM DO IT.

482
00:22:59,709 --> 00:23:01,750
- I BELIEVE YOU.

483
00:23:01,792 --> 00:23:05,750
I DON'T KNOW HOW AMON HAS
ACHIEVED THIS POWER...

484
00:23:05,792 --> 00:23:10,500
BUT THIS MEANS THE REVOLUTION
IS MORE DANGEROUS THAN EVER.

485
00:23:10,542 --> 00:23:12,125
NO BENDER IS SAFE.

486
00:23:12,166 --> 00:23:15,083
[somber music]
